- This one.

17:52.905 --> 17:53.929
Ah.

17:54.073 --> 17:55.973
I think that, uh,
there's a mistake there.

17:56.108 --> 17:57.735
There's no mistake, Fonz.

17:57.877 --> 18:00.005
