22:43.696 --> 22:45.790
Oh, Arthur,
that's really beautiful.

22:45.931 --> 22:47.831
- Thank you.
- Just beautiful.

22:47.967 --> 22:50.299
BOTH:
Merry Christmas, Joanie!

22:50.436 --> 22:52.165
